Fs restrict (cvar)
==================

Description
-----------

Restricst file system access to known .[PK4](PK4\_(file\_format)) files.

Usage
-----

At the console type...

`fs_restrictÂ [Boolean]`

Parameters
----------

-   [Boolean]
    -   0 - Allow the use of custom content.
    -   1 - Block the use of custom content.

